'''島灣'''（Bay of Islands）是位於[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]][[北島|北島]][[遠北區|遠北區]]東海岸的一個區域。島灣是紐西蘭最具人氣的釣魚、帆船和旅遊目的地區域，並且在1930年代後因美國作家贊恩·格雷的稱讚而在世界上都享有盛名。島灣內有144個天然島嶼<ref name=Hartel>{{cite journal |last=Hartel |first=Elizabeth F. |last2=Constantine |first2=Rochelle |last3=Torres |first3=Leigh G. |date=2014 |title=Changes in habitat use patterns by bottlenose dolphins over a 10-year period render static management boundaries ineffective |url= |journal=Aquatic Conservation: Marine and Freshwater Ecosystems |volume= |issue= |pages= |doi=10.1002/aqc.2465 |accessdate=25 October 2014}}</ref>。據2004年的一份研究，島灣擁有世界第二藍的天空，僅次於[[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Dumé | first = Belle | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | date = 2 August 2006 | url = http://optics.org/article/25480 | title = World's bluest sky revealed | format =  | work = Optics.org | pages =  | publisher =  | accessdate = 16 July 2012 | archive-date = 2019-02-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190205205804/http://optics.org/article/25480 }}</ref>。
